<h4 id="2-4-5-multiple-ways-aa"><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/UNDERSTANDING-WCAG20/navigation-mechanisms-mult-loc.html">2.4.5 Multiple ways (AA)</a></h4><p>Unless the service is a series of steps, there must be different ways for people to locate and navigate content. Different people will have different preferences, for example someone with a cognitive disability may prefer to browse a sitemap to locate content, whereas someone using magnification may prefer to use search instead of scrolling through a lengthy navigation block.</p>
